      <details class="fq"><summary>Is melatonin safe for kids?</summary><p>Short-term use (up to 3 months) appears safe at low doses under pediatrician guidance. The AAP supports melatonin for sleep-onset difficulties after establishing proper sleep hygiene. Long-term safety data is limited. Always consult your pediatrician.</p></details>
